#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:585
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[10]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"FLAMMABILIZER-I:\n"
"\t\t\tYour crew's fire immunity, resistance or direct healing from fire (not extinguishing) are removed! Your crew also move slower in fire, even more for each active level of Life Support (O2) on the enemy ship!"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:592
