"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[13]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"ERUPTING EARTH:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's crew resists fire, is boosted in it and generates O2 in fire, and heals while extinguishing. Your crew loses HP in fire."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:613
